data.description: Are you looking for a property with a country setting, but still want to be a short drive to the city? Well I have your home! Located only 10 minutes from Downtown Clinton, this home was built in 2020, but not totally finished and occupied until 2021. The home is brick and vinyl with a very flat .57 acre of land. Excellent layout with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Features include: LVP flooring, walk in tiled shower in the master ensuite, walk in closet in the master bedroom, farm setting with mountain views, and all appliances except the refrigerator convey. A survey on the property has been done and is in my documents. Perfect for a VA, FHA, or USDA loan. Great location! Schedule your showing today!
